Q_jHqufNoxdlgCtLbqrpsA
Giving the Big Bang four stars might be a little generous but it can be one hell of a night. I've been there a number of times to see my drunken friends get up on stage for their 21 Birthday. On the Weekend and Thursdays this will definitely be a college bar. The Piano players are good and most of the time very funny.  My biggest gripe about the Big Bang is that it tends to get old fairly quickly. It's a real novelty so after your first time, let a little time go by before your next visit.

